### Hadith 2:272

*Narrated 'Abdur Rahman bin Abi Laila:*

Only Um Hani narrated to me that she had seen the Prophet offering the
Duha prayer. She said, "On the day of the conquest of Mecca, the Prophet
entered my house, took a bath and offered eight Rakat (of Duha prayers.
I had never seen the Prophet offering such a light prayer but he
performed bowing and prostrations perfectly .

